04,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ilm: Heaven and earth praise seekers of knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Whoever travels a path in search of knowledge, Allah will make him traverse a path to Paradise. Verily, the angels lower their wings in pleasure for the seeker of knowledge. The inhabitants of the heavens and earth, even\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/18\/salaf-seeker-ilm-stop-learning\/","url_meta":{"origin":42404,"position":5},"title":"Salaf on Learning: Not befitting seeker of knowledge to stop learning","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Manadhir reported: I asked Abu 'Amr ibn al-Ala', may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cFor how long is it appropriate for a man to learn?\u201d Abu 'Amr said, \u201cIt is appropriate for him to learn his entire life.\u201d Sufyan ibn 'Uyaynah, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/42404","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\